      "role": "user",
      "content": "walk away? you mean like just leaving everything behind? i don't think you understand how permanent this feels. it’s not like i can just move to a different city and change my name. the damage is done. the people i love deserve better than a version of me that's broken and in debt. if i just... disappeared, maybe they'd eventually just remember the person i was before this, instead of looking at me with pity. isn't it better for everyone if the failure just goes away?",
